This vicious spell inflicts debilitating nighmares and pain on a target's<br>
mind often reducing them to a quivering heap.  The dark magics invade the<br>
mind, twisting and distorting the world around them, and shattering the<br>
victim both physcally and mentally.  As with most nightmare based spells,<br>
this has no effect on creatures without a mind.<br>
